Page_0: "Walking in Circles: Chapter 10

...and so Damien said to Ben, 'You are surely the foulest bastard for having written these accursed things about me.'

And Benjamin replied, 'Twere not for your selling of my soul to the heathen creatures that crawl from the depths, I would not have written these foul things about thee.'

And so did the two men become friends again, and the cycle of their adventures began anew."